ultiplayer fun with friends and family, relaxing creative gameplay, competitive tournaments, or addictive roguelite battles, this collection has something for every casual player.\n\nThe bundle also includes Bag Fight: Newman Pack, unlocking 2X Game Speed, the Newman character, the Blaster weapon, and a unique Ascension passive. On top of that, Bag Fight - Base Pack Lite gives you extra Chips, Gems, and Silver Keys to help strengthen your heroes and boost your progress.\n\nFeatures: \n• 8 full casual games in one collection \n• Local multiplayer fun in selected games \n• Fast, accessible gameplay for players of all skill levels \n• A mix of action, strategy, racing, sports, crafting, and relaxing fun \n• Colorful visuals, simple rules, and addictive challenges \n• Perfect for solo play, family game nights, and quick casual sessions \n• Extra DLC content for Bag Fight \n• Consumable pack with Chips, Gems, and Silver Keys\n\nJump into a collection full of variety, excitement, and easy-to-play fun!","developerName":"VOODOO","hasAddOns":true,"images":{"boxArt":{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fstore-images.s-microsoft.com\u002Fimage\u002Fapps.37970.13855553819051934.65671a1c-47a3-46aa-b71f-2ddcc64ce9d8.bde15f1a-7630-43db-bb69-dc9557b58b32","width":1080,"height":1080,"backgroundColor":"#FFFFFF"},"poster":{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fstore-images.s-microsoft.com\u002Fimage\u002Fapps.42039.13855553819051934.65671a1c-47a3-46aa-b71f-2ddcc64ce9d8.014b6dc8-426b-41c3-9b93-559e1fc54d19","width":720,"height":1080,"backgroundColor":"#FFFFFF"},"superHeroArt":{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fstore-images.s-microsoft.com\u002Fimage\u002Fapps.52027.13855553819051934.65671a1c-47a3-46aa-b71f-2ddcc64ce9d8.69cf0b88-14cc-447c-a802-99dae71d7dfd","width":1920,"height":1080,"backgroundColor":"#FFFFFF"}},"includedWithPassesProductIds":[],"maxInstallSize":0,"optimalSkuId":"0010","preferredSkuId":"0010","productFamily":"Games","productId":"9MVNDXV5RC3W","productKind":"Game","publisherName":"QubicGames S.A.","rati