idth":1920,"height":1080,"caption":"MLB® The Show™ 26 Storylines Trailer"}},{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fcdn.trailers.xboxservices.com\u002Ftrailers\u002F00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\u002Fis\u002Fcontent\u002Fmicrosoftassets\u002F3f7adf5b-135b-483f-8292-fd43fda74e59-AVS.m3u8?packagedStreaming=true","purpose":"trailer","height":1080,"width":1920,"title":"Fielding Feedback: Franchise","previewImage":{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fstore-images.s-microsoft.com\u002Fimage\u002Fapps.16783.14385377751056556.45a6dec8-2a85-4eda-adb8-cfe52fa49ab3.d8761a30-32b0-4132-8e1c-0bda42578877","width":1920,"height":1080,"caption":"Fielding Feedback: Franchise"}},{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fcdn.trailers.xboxservices.com\u002Ftrailers\u002F00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\u002Fis\u002Fcontent\u002Fmicrosoftassets\u002Ff4cf567e-081d-4dbd-abd6-371824321a45-AVS.m3u8?packagedStreaming=true","purpose":"trailer","height":1080,"width":1920,"title":"Fielding Feedback: Gameplay Updates","previewImage":{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fstore-images.s-microsoft.com\u002Fimage\u002Fapps.30418.14385377751056556.45a6dec8-2a85-4eda-adb8-cfe52fa49ab3.bef0b729-7593-42d4-973d-f2eacc41b1ee","width":1920,"height":1080,"caption":"Fielding Feedback: Gameplay Updates"}}],"xCloudProperties":{"xCloudId":"MLBTHESHOW26","xboxTitleId":1791650399,"supportsTouch":false},"passMetadataByPassProductId":{},"xCloudPropertiesV2":{"xCloudId":"MLBTHESHOW26","xboxTitleId":1791650399,"programs":["GPULTIMATE","CALLISTO","DIA","EUROPA","TRITON"],"supportedInputTypes":["Controller"],"supportsTouch":false},"isAvailableOnGarrison":false,"hasUbisoftCrossEntitlementProduct":false},"9NWZPS8X9JQG":{"availableOn":["XboxSeriesX","PC"],"averageRating":0,"badges":[],"categories":["Role playing","Action & adventure","Simulation","Strategy"],"contentRating":{"boardName":"IARC","description":"For ages 16 and up","disclaimers":[],"descriptors":["Strong Violence"],"imageUri":"https:\u002F\u002Fstore-images.s-microsoft.com\u002Fimage\u002Fglobal.23519.image.809064e2-5b97-451f-bd04-e3cbd042ddcc.ce30c715-a977-48f0-9929-0dee0e170626","imageLinkUri":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.globalratings.com\u002F","interactiveDescriptions":[],"rating":"16+","ratingAge":16,"ratingDescription":"For ages 16 and up"},"description":"Framed for the murder of the Prince and sentenced to death by the Crown, you've been living in the shadows ever since. After barely dodging an attempt on your life, you find the assassin's contract that raises many questions - was it just misfortune that you were framed? Or is there more to it? Determined to find the answers, you journey back to the very place you escaped. \n\nSlowly but surely, you will lead a rebellion against your homeland's oppressive Sovereign to victory, uncovering the truth of your family's secret along the way. The bells shall ring for freedom once again! \n\nEstablish and expand your own settlements, liberate the land and assist its villagers, and recruit others to your cause while learning more about a life you had to leave behind. Your recruits will help you build up the resources and might needed for a stand against the Crown. Command your forces, prove your valor through combat, and cement yourself as the hero of your people.\n\nKey Features:\n\nSurvive and Explore - Gather, hunt, build and craft! Collect and manage resources in a harsh world to survive, and journey through the land for its secrets and adventures! The Crown and its Royal Army is not the only foe in the kingdom…\n\nConquer and Expand - Work your way up from a small camp to becoming the leader of a great rebellion. Improve your relations with the settlements, grow your armies, and liberate regions from the Crown to strengthen your cause. Gain followers with unique knowledge along the way  and find new resources to further the technologies of your towns.\n\nResource and Town Management - As you free the villages from the oppressive influence of the Crown, build, manage, and upgrade your own outposts and towns with the help of your recruits. Organize your workers and train the strongest soldiers in the kingdom to grow the rebellion.\n\nSkill-Based Directional Combat - Choose your equipment from a variety of medieval weapons and armor. From swords and axes to heavy mauls and polearms, and bows, choose your unique style of fighting and hone your skill in directional combat.\n\nArmy Command - Lead your armies into battle, commanding your squads and formations, and employ cunning tactics to your advantage. Equip and train your troops the way you want it, and control them on the battlefield to prove your skill and might. \n\nDeep Progression - Improve your own skills in combat and survival, train your soldiers and see your workers become master craftsmen. Each new recruit will bring unique knowledge to the table, from crafting better arrows to building advanced structures in your town, so choose wisely. Opportunities for growth are endless!\n\nStory and Roleplay - As you expand your armies and influence across the land, unravel your family secrets and learn the truth behind the terrible death of the Prince you were accused of murdering. The mysteries of the kingdom await…","developerName":"Donkey Crew","hasAddOns":false,"hhVerified":{"deviceEvaluation":2},"images":{"boxArt":{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fstore-images.s-microsoft.com\u002Fimage\u002Fapps.11289.14435552270902845.ec3cf6ff-e660-4d4a-abbc-0ad60cd4d3eb.ed4a8782-2aa5-4235-99c4-2c29ef41c28e","width":2160,"height":2160},"poster":{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fstore-images.s-microsoft.com\u002Fimage\u002Fapps.65451.14435552270902845.ec3cf6ff-e660-4d4a-abbc-0ad60cd4d3eb.cd544984-ed44-4285-9c33-ee43e4762179","width":1440,"height":2160},"superHeroArt":{"url":"https:\u002F\u002Fstore-images.s-microsoft.com\u002Fimage\u002Fapps.58544.14435552270902845.ec3cf6ff-e660-4d4a-abbc-0ad60cd4d3eb.77417143-6e75-41da-87ee-4d7ffa9ebe14","width":3840,"height":2160}},"includedWithPassesProductIds":[],"maxInstallSize":0,"optimalSkuId":"0010","preferredSkuI